## Quality Gates

Before marking verification complete:

- ✅ All step command files have `<verification>` blocks
- ✅ Schema is parseable (valid markdown tables)
- ✅ All file paths are valid
- ✅ Score calculation is accurate
- ✅ Gaps have actionable fix recommendations
- ✅ Auto-fixable gaps can be automatically resolved

