## Integration with Workflow

**Before @dev-loop:**
```bash
@step-verify --step=1-9 --fix    # Ensure all planning steps complete (includes 1.5 if monetized)
@dev-loop --from=F01             # Then start implementation
```

**After completing a step:**
```bash
@step-1-ideation                 # Run the step
@step-verify --step=1            # Verify completion
```

**After Step 1 (monetized projects):**
